01:45:32.832 --> 01:45:36.043
You press here to record
and you press here to play.

01:45:36.127 --> 01:45:38.462
<i>There's
also the matter of the $140,000</i>

01:45:38.546 --> 01:45:39.713
<i>that seems to have walked away</i>

01:45:39.797 --> 01:45:42.550
<i>from the Madrugada cheque-cashing bust.</i>

01:45:42.716 --> 01:45:44.969
<i>I didn't have anything
to do with that, so...</i>

01:45:45.052 --> 01:45:47.138
<i>We'd like to be
in your corner on that.</i>

