<i>In exchange for what? I mean, what,
do you want me to do something unethical?</i>

01:45:50.141 --> 01:45:52.101
<i>I mean, no disrespect to the both of youse</i>

01:45:52.184 --> 01:45:54.228
<i>but I don't need you
to be in my corner, Mr Mayor.</i>

01:45:54.311 --> 01:45:55.646
<i>Look, I'm innocent.</i>

01:45:55.729 --> 01:45:58.482
<i>Innocent or guilty,
you're still going down.</i>

01:45:59.316 --> 01:46:03.320
<i>Give Miss White whatever
she needs, or your career is over.</i>

01:46:03.779 --> 01:46:04.905
<i>Done.</i>

01:46:05.281 --> 01:46:06.490
<i>Kaput.</i>

01:46:07.992 --> 01:46:10.953
