- Sorry.
- Excuse me.

02:02:28.722 --> 02:02:30.349
<i>Why don't you
just walk out the door?</i>

02:02:30.432 --> 02:02:31.517
<i>I will.</i>

02:02:31.767 --> 02:02:34.645
<i>I'm gonna walk out of that door
when I'm good and ready.</i>

